rComments: Great professor. He takes the time to get to know the students personally, and remembers their names, even in the 60+ student lecture room. The lectures are interesting, and he makes sure we are doing well in the class. Gives us plenty of time to study and prepare, and tells us exactly what we're gonna expect on the exams. I ended up with an A+!

He led the discussion section and was fairly enthusiastic despite a total lack of interest or effort from most students during discussions. He's a good guy and takes time to have extra office hours around exam times.
